title: Dick Clark Interviews Cannonball Adderly- American Bandstand
fulltitle: Dick Clark Interviews Cannonball Adderly- American Bandstand
description: Dick Clark interviews Cannonball Adderly and the band, and talks about the success of the song, "Mercy, Mercy, Mercy," and how it's the biggest selling record they've had yet.
